#          doublestar, ~250M go.sum downloads, foundational
#          dependency of hashicorp/copywrite (R607) + snyk/
#          driftctl (2.6k stars) + ZupIT/horusec (1.3k stars) +
#          mutagen-io/mutagen (4.2k stars) + camptocamp/
#          terraboard (2k stars) + yusufcanb/tlm (THIS) + 1500+
#          Go applications using ** glob patterns for path
